description:
It's time to once again show the world that The Samurai aren't just a bunch of goofy people who play and enjoy video games. We are here to help save and aid as many people as possible, SO: Another Charity Livestream is coming! Tomorrow (3/19/2017), I will be streaming to hopefully raise $14,000 so less fortunate people around the world can have access to fresh clean water.

https://my.charitywater.org/coryxkenshin/samurai-special

Feel free to start donating now, or you can wait until the stream (will have awesome donation pop-ups... hopefully lol)
